<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e53e3e 0%, #c53030 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
        .event-details {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #e53e3e;
        }
        .alert-box {
            background: #fee2e2;
            border: 2px solid #e53e3e;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>❌ Event Cancelled</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <strong>{{ studentName }}</strong>,</p>
        
        <p>We regret to inform you that the following event has been <strong>cancelled</strong>:</p>
        
        <div class="event-details">
            <h2>📅 {{ eventName }}</h2>
            <p><strong>Team:</strong> {{ teamName }}</p>
            <p><strong>Originally scheduled:</strong> {{ eventDate|date('F d, Y \\a\\t H:i') }}</p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{ eventLocation }}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="alert-box">
            <h3 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #991b1b;">⚠️ Important Notice</h3>
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #991b1b; font-weight: bold;">
                This event will NOT take place. Please do not go to the venue.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <p><strong>What happens next?</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>✅ Your registration has been automatically cancelled</li>
            <li>✅ No action is required from you</li>
            <li>✅ Watch for announcements about future events</li>
            <li>✅ We apologize for any inconvenience</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>We understand this may be disappointing. We'll notify you as soon as new events are scheduled!</p>
        
        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; font-size: 16px; color: #667eea; font-weight: bold;">
            📧 Stay tuned for upcoming events!
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Autolearn Platform - Your Learning Journey</p>
        <p>This is an automated email, please do not reply.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
